INSERT INTO met_news VALUES('15','Why enterprise to build many languages, multilingual enterprise web site?','Why enterprise to build many languages, multilingual enterprise web site?','Internet has grown in strength, has become a business and individuals to seek business opportunities for goods, services and information to understand the preferred way. From the standpoint of enhancing competitive advantage of an enterprise perspective, construction of a multi-language website is the premise of ever-increasing number of customers and increase sales of efficient means.\r\n','<p>\r\n	&nbsp;Internet has grown in strength, has become a business and individuals to seek business opportunities for goods, services and information to understand the preferred way. From the standpoint of enhancing competitive advantage of an enterprise perspective, construction of a multi-language website is the premise of ever-increasing number of customers and increase sales of efficient means.<br />\r\n	With the accelerating process of internationalization, multilingual website will become an integral part of businesses and organizations.<br />\r\n	Multi-language Web site to help companies face a number of Internet users of non-English speaking countries<br />\r\n	Over time, non-English speaking countries the proportion of Internet users has been on the rise. Compared to the previous control by the English-speaking Internet users has produced a fundamental change in the situation. Nelson Group (an American Internet research and consulting firm) in March 2005 about: Foreign Internet market is &quot;going to the mature fruit&quot;, as long as you are willing to pay less effort to be able to get a huge harvest. The results showed that the growth of the Internet in the United States, Germany, Britain and Sweden tend to slow, and in other countries such as France, Hong Kong, Italy and Japan grew significantly.<br />\r\n	Nelson, a senior analyst explained: &quot;The most readily available opportunities in the country&#39;s Internet use habits and the user (or site) before the relationship was established. In the current growth stage of training will become loyal customer base of customers . &quot;multi-language Web site is an effective marketing tool for companies for most Internet users have the ability to use their own language to communicate, which means more than the increase in sales, more valuable in the local market to build on your brand, service, and products known.<br />\r\n	Construction of multi-language Web site is a great program, because it is likely that companies marketing to capture new customers, establish new customer relationships and to give the brand an international image of the most effective way.<br />\r\n	Multi-language website can bring new customers for the enterprise<br />\r\n	By exposing your multi-language Web site in various countries and regions in front of potential customers, naturally, you get the native language the user&#39;s attention.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Multi-language Web site to increase sales for businesses<br />\r\n	On the site may each additional language has the potential to double sales. Even if only the site contains only into Spanish, French, German and Italian language of the four world&#39;s major sites, and its sales could also potentially increase 4 times. This is a rare use of such a small investment to obtain such a large effect.<br />\r\n	Multi-language Web site to convey the customer-centric service awareness<br />\r\n	Multi-language Web site shows your customers that you are thinking. Your customer-centric thinking and customer efforts to care for the customer will be grateful, because the extra work you, they will be more inclined to patronize your business.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Multi-language Web site to get more confidence<br />\r\n	Number of transactions executed through the Internet are often not familiar with each other as the language of each resulting trust between different cultures. Provided to the customer the choice of multiple languages ​​to help them feel safe, they know exactly how to trade, with whom transactions.<br />\r\n	Multi-language Web site to help overcome the cultural sensitivity<br />\r\n	After a proper design of a multi-language Web sites, the target market through the use of local languages ​​to overcome potential cultural barriers. Automatic multi-language Web site for customers to create a &quot;cultural comfort zone&quot; so that they can freely navigate, understand site information, and interact with you.<br />\r\n	Multi-language Web site to effectively combat competitors<br />\r\n	Gain a competitive advantage in today&#39;s environment requires thinking out of the frame. Many companies try to distinguish themselves from competitors. Observation of your competitors, if they multilingual website why do you not? If they do not, why not lead the market first before they build your company&#39;s brand?</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Multi-language web site for the international style of business<br />\r\n	A multilingual Web site to display your ideas, business and international business processes. International corporate image and establish industry leadership in this multi-language Web site to help regional countries for different search engines<br />\r\n	Search engines will bring people to your site. However, in some countries and regions have their own popular search engines, these search engines are mainly based on the use of mother tongue to work habits to adapt to people&#39;s needs, it was a success. Search Engine type engine is the key to open the local market, in addition, unless they can use a specific language (such as English) would be difficult to find you.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	In addition, many keyword search engines, particularly Google, in the excellent multi-language capability development. Multi-language Web site has a page to maximize the protection of your site can search by many search engines and display. Services are constantly shift and change. The current multi-language Web site is still in early stages, many multinational companies use multi-language Web site to consolidate its international status. However, the next impact will occur naturally, multilingual website will become the main part of the Internet. Regardless of business is to choose now or in the future, this is the only option for website construction.</p>\r\n','33','46','0','0','0','0','','','1','admin','0','2011-05-19 17:10:39','2011-05-19 09:59:58','0','0','','en');
INSERT INTO met_news VALUES('16','Web site promotion company with the advantage of','Web site promotion company with the advantage of','70.54% of Internet users concentrated in the more developed regions, 64% of family income above 1000 yuan, 85.8% aged 18 to 35 years old, 83% had a university or higher education. Therefore, the network is the propaganda of the target groups in society at the highest level, the highest income, the highest spending power of the most dynamic consumer groups. This group is often greater than the total consumption of other consumer level and.\r\n','<p>\r\n	1, the network is multi-dimensional promotional publicity<br />\r\n	Traditional media is two-dimensional, and network information is multidimensional, it can be text, images and sound together organic, multi-sensory transfer of information, immersive experience for customers such as goods or services. So that consumers can experience the products, services and brands. This picture, text, sound, like a combination of forms of propaganda to enhance the effectiveness of the network information.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	2, the network information with the most dynamic consumer groups<br />\r\n	70.54% of Internet users concentrated in the more developed regions, 64% of family income above 1000 yuan, 85.8% aged 18 to 35 years old, 83% had a university or higher education. Therefore, the network is the propaganda of the target groups in society at the highest level, the highest income, the highest spending power of the most dynamic consumer groups. This group is often greater than the total consumption of other consumer level and.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	3, the network media productions, low cost, speed, flexibility to change<br />\r\n	Propaganda short production cycles, even in the short run cycle can also be completed soon, according to the needs of production, the high cost of traditional media productions, put on a fixed period. Also, advertise in traditional media is difficult to change even after the release can be changed very often have to pay the economic price. Advertise on the internet, customers need in a timely manner in accordance with changes in information content. Thus, changes in management decision can be immediately implemented and promoted.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	4, Propaganda and the depth of interactive<br />\r\n	Strong interaction is the Internet&#39;s largest advantage of the media, which is different from the one-way dissemination of information in traditional media, but the interactive information dissemination. Through the link, the user simply clicks the mouse to the relevant site from the manufacturers to get more and more detailed information. In addition, users can fill out and submit the online network directly form information, vendors can have ready access to valuable user feedback, further reducing the user and the distance between the customer information. At the same time, the network can provide further product information query requirements.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	5, the network can be improved statistical information<br />\r\n	&quot;What can not be measured can not manage.&quot; Network information through timely and accurate statistical mechanisms to enable users to publish information directly on-line monitoring. The traditional forms of information dissemination is not accurate only by ratings, circulation, etc. to statistics put the number of audience.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	6, the network information to track and measure the effect of publicity<br />\r\n	Internet users can instantly measure the effect of publicity. Propaganda by monitoring page views, click-through rate and other indicators, the user can see statistics of how many people have the information released, including how many people are interested in further information on the release of information to further understand the details. Therefore, compared with any other promotion, web promotion enable users to better track the audience&#39;s reaction, keep abreast of the situation of users and potential users.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	7, the network run more targeted publicity<br />\r\n	By providing many free services, web users can often establish a complete database, including the user&#39;s geographical distribution, age, gender, income, occupation, marital status, hobbies and so on. This information can help users analyze the market and the audience, according to the characteristics of the target audience information release, targeted release of information and features for the user point of delivery and tracking of delivery to make objective and accurate evaluation of results.<br />\r\n	In addition, the network can also provide targeted promotional content environment. Different sites or different channels of the same Web site services provided by a different class quality and has a strong, respectively, and this closely to meet the user&#39;s interest as possible.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	8, the network audience interest advocacy and high<br />\r\n	According to information, television and people can not focus the attention of the audience, while 40% read, 21% of the people while doing housework, 13% of people eating and drinking, 12% of people enjoying it in the matter, 10% In cooking, 9% in writing, 8% of the phone. While 55% of online users in the use of computer it do not do anything, only 6% while on the phone, only 5% in food and drink, only 4% in writing.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	9, the network delivery of media propaganda to shorten the process<br />\r\n	Users of traditional media marketing efforts generally go through three stages: market development, the market consolidation and market maintenance phase. In all three phases, the manufacturer must first obtain the attention, the creation of brand awareness; brand in consumers preliminary information, the promotion of more detailed product information. And then more firmly established and the link between consumers, to build brand loyalty. The Internet combined these three stages is implemented in an information release: consumers see the Internet publicity, clicks for more information and complete user information or directly involved in market activities and even direct the user to implement online purchasing behavior.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	10, the network disseminate a wide range of information, regardless of time limits<br />\r\n	Through the Internet, network promotional messages can be transmitted 24 hours a day to every corner of the world. Provided they have Internet access, anyone, anywhere can read. This is the traditional media can not be achieved.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	11, the network information with repeatability and accessibility<br />\r\n	Propaganda can be text, voice, picture perfect combination for the user to take the initiative to search after repeated viewing. And it is compared to TV users passively accept advertising. If you miss the publicity of time, you can not get published information. In addition, it is obvious propaganda than the network information retrieval to retrieve the plane time-consuming, troublesome and more.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	12, the network information has a price advantage<br />\r\n	From price considerations, and newspapers and magazines or television compared to the current network is still relatively cheap publicity costs. Receive the same publicity effect, the effective cost per thousand advertising network is far lower than traditional advertising media. The annual cost of a promotional page is approximately a few thousand yuan, and the page content can change with the business decision-making change at any time, it is inconceivable traditional advertising media. Network marketing campaign will become an indispensable and efficient way.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n','33','47','0','1','0','0','','','1','admin','1','2011-05-19 17:22:11','2011-05-18 20:57:46','0','0','','en');
